Documentation will be here soon.

EXAMPLE.

    # test.py

    import pack

    def hello(req, name):
      return "Hello, %s." % name

    routes = def_routes(
      GET('^/hello/(.+)/?$', hello),
      GET('^/goodbye/(.+)/?$', "Bye!")
    )

    app = pack(routes)

Magic:

    $ gunicorn test:app

(Green Unicorn <http://gunicorn.org> is a good WSGI server.)